<!-- --------------- About V-Link --------------- -->
<div style="width:100%;background-color:#ccc" id="aboutus">
    <div class="container about">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h1 style="padding: 10px 30px; font-size: 28px; color: blue;">About Vacancy Links</h1>
                <p style="padding: 10px 30px; text-align: justify;">
                    <span style="color: blue">Vacancy Links</span> is a premier executive recruitment search
                    website, located in <span style="color: blue">Yangon, Myanmar</span>. We focus on senior
                    to executive level recruitment, as well as experts in headhunting and background checking.
                    Our recruitment consultants have extensive recruitment, as well as industry experience in
                    a variety of sectors from leading institutions in Myanmar. Our value comes from the
                    ability to attract, select, and retain the most talented people in the market through our
                    industry leading technology and vast professional networks.<br />
                    Regional leaders look to us to advise them not only on recruitment matters in Myanmar,
                    but also work with them as partners to plan and execute their business visions. We act
                    as partners to ensure that our clients don't need to worry about their recruitment plans,
                    so that they can focus on what they do best.<br />
                </p>
            </div>
